# PED::RESET_AI_WEAPON_DAMAGE_MODIFIER

## Summary
Resets the damage modifier when ai is inflicting weapon damage

## Description
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
This function will reset the ai weapon damage multiplier
